<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddb7f9c8c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s1449"><num value="1449">§ 1449.</num><heading> Reservation of right to amend or repeal chapter</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The right to alter, amend, or repeal this chapter is expressly reserved.</p>
